{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"1972","heading":"Genius Prize for Save Our Seas Innovations","label":"1972 Genius Prize for Save Our Seas Innovations","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/ch33A/schIII","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs1972","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","CodificationSection was formerly classified to prior to renumbering by .section 4232 of this titlePub. L. 119–65"],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"In general","label":"a In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs1972%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"In general","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs1972%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/a/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/a/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs1972%2Fa%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"to encourage technological innovation with the potential to reduce plastic waste, and associated and potential pollution, and thereby prevent marine debris; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/a/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/a/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs1972%2Fa%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"to award 1 or more prizes biennially for projects that advance human understanding and innovation in removing and preventing plastic waste, in one of the categories described in paragraph (2).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Categories for projects","label":"2 Categories for projects","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs1972%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/a/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs1972%2Fa%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Advancements in materials used in packaging and other products that, if such products enter the coastal or ocean environment, will fully degrade without harming the environment, wildlife, or human health.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/a/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs1972%2Fa%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Innovations in production and packaging design that reduce the use of raw materials, increase recycled content, encourage reusability and recyclability, and promote a circular economy.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/a/2/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs1972%2Fa%2F2%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Improvements in marine debris detection, monitoring, and cleanup technologies and processes.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"D","heading":null,"label":"D","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/a/2/D","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs1972%2Fa%2F2%2FD","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Improvements or improved strategies to increase solid waste collection, processing, sorting, recycling, or reuse.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"E","heading":null,"label":"E","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/a/2/E","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs1972%2Fa%2F2%2FE","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"New designs or strategies to reduce overall packaging needs and promote reuse.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Designation","label":"b Designation","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs1972%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The prize competition established under subsection (a) shall be known as the “Genius Prize for Save Our Seas Innovations”.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Prioritization","label":"c Prioritization","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs1972%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs1972%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"have a strategy, submitted with the application or proposal, to move the new technology, process, design, material, or other product supported by the prize to market-scale deployment;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs1972%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"support the concept of a circular economy; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/c/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs1972%2Fc%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/c/3/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/c/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs1972%2Fc%2F3%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"can fully degrade in the ocean without harming the environment, wildlife, or human health; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/c/3/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1972/c/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs1972%2Fc%2F3%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"are to be used in fishing gear or other maritime products that have an increased likelihood of entering the coastal or ocean environment as unintentional waste.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}]}
